   The workshop pad layout in `librelane/slots/slot_workshop.yaml`
   is a port of that configuration file from the standalone padring
   tool into a LibreLane slot definition. The pad ordering (60
   analog + 20 bidir + 4/4 DVDD/DVSS + clk + rst_n + corners) and
   the die size (2935 × 2935 µm) follow Juan Moya's design; the
   LibreLane-specific encoding is ours.

